{"tid":2166023,"cid":8,"subCid":0,"title":"有冇師兄覺得有啲宅男，仲衰過啲職場老屎忽","createTime":"2020-08-20T07:31:41.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-20T12:59:45.000Z","uid":105678,"like":10,"dislike":20,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"0ed1cd9cc613155e76d1f11e0b6a7b02165c4635","tid":2166023,"uid":105678,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-20T07:31:41.000Z","msg":"講翻少少背景，我本身都係動漫迷來(會去漫展嗰種)<br />\n<br />\n咁呢排就畀公司調左去另一個department啦，入面啲人幾乎都係格仔衫長陰咁嘅<br />\n<br />\n有時聽佢地講動漫都幾技入，咁我本身睇開都同佢地討論下啦<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />：我<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />：宅男同事<br />\n<br />\n我：你地都睇開動畫架，我都有睇喎！<br />\n<br />\n宅男同事：你睇開乜呀<br />\n<br />\n我：呢排追鬼滅之刃呀，牙炭好型彌豆子都得意！<br />\n<br />\n宅男同事：下鬼滅？Taste咁差嘅<br />\n<br />\n我：...我仲有睇開鋼煉架，神作級，講哲學好有深度！<br />\n<br />\n宅男同事：屌垃圾咪拎嚟講啦，攻殻、進擊的巨人呢啲就真哲學啦，唔識唔好扮識啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n我：......(唔識應)<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n最後佢全日都對住我黑口黑面，好似殺左佢全家咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3e137af832f6af5a5d5af1eb45937acaffcdb95f","tid":2166023,"uid":128102,"like":9,"dislike":2,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-20T07:33:11.000Z","msg":"唔識唔好扮識啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3f240d5d9cc4323459a9d3f96f1652fd795710c8","tid":2166023,"uid":191467,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-20T07:34:26.000Z","msg":"做咩又post多次?"},{"pid":"d50e5ed5e959a4d709211453155eef374e0558bb","tid":2166023,"uid":105678,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"3f240d5d9cc4323459a9d3f96f1652fd795710c8","tid":2166023,"uid":191467,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-20T07:34:26.000Z","msg":"做咩又post多次?"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-20T07:35:04.000Z","msg":"再拉送你去見上帝"},{"pid":"c78da2160afd46268869df7774ee9e71d798195e","tid":2166023,"uid":191467,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"d50e5ed